  27 Nov 2007; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  streamdvd-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed quoting.

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  10 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add missing email address for herd with name != alias.

  31 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/streamdvd-0.4-libdvdread.patch, streamdvd-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Add patch from Alexis Ballier to build with latest libdvdread, see bug #128224.

  15 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> -streamdvd-0.3.ebuild,
  -streamdvd-0.4.ebuild:
  Drop old versions.

  15 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/streamdvd-0.4-gcc41.patch, +files/streamdvd-0.4-makefile.patch,
  metadata.xml, streamdvd-0.3.ebuild, streamdvd-0.4.ebuild,
  streamdvd-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Add patches to build with gcc 4.1 and to respect compiler and flags
  variables; also fix --as-needed usage. Closes bug #126291.

  30 Oct 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  streamdvd-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Added missing lsdvd dependency as per bug #104375.

  03 Sep 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  streamdvd-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Don't install COPYING file.

  23 Jan 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> streamdvd-0.4-r1.ebuild:
